title: Trendeo NoHo 10/18: Dennis Prager, Colin Powell, Indiana Jones 5, MacBook Pro, Candace Parker, Christopher Steele
itunes:title: Trendeo NoHo 10/18: Dennis Prager, Colin Powell, Indiana Jones 5, MacBook Pro, Candace Parker, Christopher Steele
description:
In this edition of Trendeo NoHo, Jack and Miles discuss Dennis Prager getting COVID, war criminal Colin Powell dying of COVID complications, tentpole movies getting pushed back even more, the new MacBook Pro, Candace Parker leading Chicago Sky to first WNBA championship, and former spy Christopher Steele defending Trump/Russia dossier.
